race.comment: HERE'S HOPING (1) has been out of the placings the last couple but was a Maiden winner (20.27) three back at this track. Has the ability and looks a key chance here. GREAT MARLOW (7) comes off an average effort last start when sixth at this track over 350m behind Impress Amber (20.98) in a Grade 5. Better than the latest run and deserves another chance. WHISKEY AND WINE (2) has a moderate overall strike-rate. Finished second (20.27) at this track latest and might be close to finding winning form again. Solid record at the distance winning five races. Comes through a solid form race last start. Hard to beat again. ROBELL POLLY (4) has ability and can feature with the right run after missing a cheque here most recently.
